title: Austin Park Meetup
description: Let's meet up at the Austin Park this weekend and let our furry friends run loose! Water will be provided for both humans and pets!

title: Downtown Group Dog Walking
description: Interested in going for a walk downtown while making new friends? Meet in front of the Austin capital!

title: Paws in the Park
description: Join us for a fun day of play at Zilker Park! We'll have frisbees, balls, and treats for all the furry attendees.

title: Canine Carnival
description: Step right up to the Canine Carnival! There will be games, prizes, and lots of tail-wagging fun for all dogs.

title: Pup Picnic
description: Pack your favorite treats and join us for a laid-back picnic at Pease Park. Dogs and humans alike are welcome to relax and enjoy.

title: Barktoberfest
description: Celebrate Barktoberfest at the Austin Pet Expo! Enjoy pet-friendly vendors, contests, and more.

title: Paws & Paint
description: Unleash your pet's inner artist at our Paws & Paint event. We'll provide the paint, canvases, and plenty of fun!

title: Howl-O-Ween Costume Party
description: Join us for a spooktacular Howl-O-Ween costume party! Dress up your furry friend and enjoy games, treats, and a pet costume contest.

title: Trail Tails Hike
description: Embark on a scenic hike with your four-legged companion. We'll explore the beautiful Greenbelt Trail and enjoy nature together.

title: Thanksgiving Pawrade
description: Join us for a festive Thanksgiving Pawrade through downtown Austin! Dress up your pets in holiday-themed attire and spread cheer.

title: Jingle Paws 5K
description: Get into the holiday spirit with the Jingle Paws 5K! Walk or run with your pet along the Lady Bird Lake Trail and support a good cause.

title: Frosty Paws Winter Wonderland
description: Celebrate the winter season at the Frosty Paws Winter Wonderland. Enjoy snow, games, and hot cocoa for both humans and pets!

title: New Year's Pup Party
description: Ring in the new year with a Pup Party! There will be music, games, and a countdown to a 'pawsome' 2024.

title: Valentine's Day Playdate
description: Spread the love with a Valentine's Day playdate at Lovey Park. Bring your pets and enjoy themed activities and treats.
